title: Little Rock volleyball team wins at Georgia State
text:
Little Rock volleyball team wins in 4 sets at Georgia State THE ASSOCIATED PRESS   4:43   4:44   
Subjects: 
Georgia (561) 

LITTLE ROCK, Arkansas â€” The Little Rock Trojans volleyball team has won a four-set match at Georgia State. 
The Trojans claimed a 25-23, 18-25, 25-21, 25-23 win over Georgia State Sunday in Atlanta. 
Little Rock improves to 8-10 overall and 4-4 in the Sun Belt Conference while GSU falls to 4-13 on the season and 0-7 in the conference.
